    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>The ManipulateMachine state machine performs the manipulation part of the storing groceries challenge:
- Inspect the table
- State item
- Grab item
- State item
- Grab item
- Drive to cabinet
- State place shelf
- Place item
- State place shelf
- Place item
</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
